@startuml
title Botica POS MediZano - Tiempo
robust "Cajero" as Cajero
robust "Frontend" as FE
robust "API" as API
robust "Stock" as Stock
robust "Comprobante" as Comp
@0
Cajero is Autenticado
FE is Listo
API is Disponible
Stock is Disponible
Comp is Pendiente
@5
Cajero is BuscandoProducto
FE is Consultando
API is Validando
@10
Cajero is ConfirmandoVenta
FE is CalculandoTotal
API is RegistrandoVenta
Stock is Reservado
@15
Cajero is Cobrando
API is ConfirmandoPago
Stock is Descontado
Comp is Generando
@20
Cajero is Finalizado
FE is ComprobanteVisible
API is Disponible
Comp is Emitido
@enduml
